condense_params_vax.Rd

condense vaxified parameters to base parameters

condense_params_vax(params)

Arguments

params

vaxified parameters (e.g. generated with `expand_params_vax()`)

Value

an object of class `params_pansim`

Examples

condense_params_vax(expand_params_vax(read_params("PHAC.csv")))
